rinken. Ze worden gevolgd door de grootste trots in het hele Ruaha National Park, de Baobab-trots.","category":"Documentaire, Natuur"},"3035964":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:natgeowild","start":"1627345500","end":"1627348500","first":"L","idtitle":"LIONKINGDOM","title":"Lion Kingdom","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F7e4d2255-315e-4ac7-9a2b-08445c14dcba,imi:ad5551803dd9456a23eeebbf0a08c625e75f9e45","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/4a1__4a2__4a14a2f8-4f05-4600-8fdc-d2abe9bb4925__B151214235.jpg","description":"The Glade is een paradijs waar altijd water is, een plek waar vreemde dingen gebeuren. Terwijl de droogte in Ruaha voortduurt, komen kuddes olifanten in de open plek. Ze graven met hun slurfen diep in het zand om het schoonste water te kunnen drinken.","category":"Documentaire, Natuur"},"3036068":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:natgeowild","start":"1627348500","end":"1627351200","first":"A","idtitle":"ANIMALFIGHTCLUB","title":"Animal Fight Club","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F7e010a45-092c-4aee-9f3c-176055275ca6,imi:b5e1b6b89249f8eeba63c1065720ce6019172e7e","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/91d__09b__91d09b62-b7ad-4163-aa38-63593904c335__B141404110.jpg","description":"In deze dynamische aflevering is het jagers versus prooi, moordenaars versus moordenaar, en vechten de slachtoffers terug.","category":"Documentaire, Natuur"},"3036877":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:natgeowild","start":"1627351200","end":"1627353900","first":"A","idtitle":"ANIMALFIGHTCLUB","title":"Animal Fight Club","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2Fe9a8b540-f1d0-4867-98fb-9b70382e0267,imi:aa76e07da68c2f54807d0288d4919a910c622787","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/91d__09b__91d09b62-b7ad-4163-aa38-63593904c335__B141404110.jpg","description":"Van grijze 